  canal trust and river thames alliance suchet is vice - president of the lichfield and hatherton canals trust , whose most challenging achievement to date has been securing funding ( both via an appeal and from influencing government decisions ) concerning the building of the new m6 toll motorway where it cuts the lines of the lichfield canal and the hatherton canal , both of which the trust wishes to see reopened .

